{"tid":2297216,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：古早手機 趕絕安心保平安  網民問創科局點強裝（李八方）","createTime":"2020-11-23T06:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T06:58:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"86a5a916985e42ebec830bece3fdb3bd80364938","tid":2297216,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:16:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201123/M7OJJST6BFBK5PI6BVORF3YZ4E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201123%2FM7OJJST6BFBK5PI6BVORF3YZ4E%2F&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnbHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=bf8904d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201123%2FM7OJJST6BFBK5PI6BVORF3YZ4E%2F&h=bd42fc24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201123/M7OJJST6BFBK5PI6BVORF3YZ4E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：古早手機 趕絕安心保平安 <br />\n網民問創科局點強裝（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KfpuMeiq_KpWiaTbP4k_bowRJLU=/1276x1436/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/W5ECO27GIZCFLGUFEU7XIA7TBM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKfpuMeiq_KpWiaTbP4k_bowRJLU%3D%2F1276x1436%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FW5ECO27GIZCFLGUFEU7XIA7TBM.jpg&h=720e886a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府上星期推出「安心出行」app，好多人恥笑個名好似「安心偷食」出軌事件，個app喺推出首日仲被發現Android版過度收集手機私隱，令市民對個app反應更冷淡。創科局長薛永恒可能怕交唔到功課，前日再獻新猷，聲稱不排除強制市民裝app。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n最先挑薛永恒機嘅係「前線科技人員」小編，佢哋喺facebook出po，表示好心急想下載「安心偷食」，但點搵都搵唔到，搞到唔敢出街，猛問局長點算好？八方睇佢哋貼嘅智能手機相，原來係一部「史前」手機Palm phone嚟，呢部手機既唔係行Android，又唔係行iOS，係行PalmOS系統，而且部手機仲可以正常使用。唔講唔知，PalmOS系統90年代推出時仲紅過蘋果公司產品，好多網友留言都話好想出返部新機，用嚟避開監控簡直一流，仲講笑話應該有炒價。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ubx1_bFkkaQY7zKScQE2Ij7NxQs=/378x1273/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EV6DRB5YNRE37BKDNFHYOZZLVE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUbx1_bFkkaQY7zKScQE2Ij7NxQs%3D%2F378x1273%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEV6DRB5YNRE37BKDNFHYOZZLVE.jpg&h=07ec4bad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■舊款機如Nokia 3310及Palm未能安裝「安心出行」app。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「拎部Nokia出街算唔算犯法?」<br />\n<br />\n「前線科技人員」笑完薛永恒，到連燈仔接力，個個拎晒Nokia 3310等各系列手機出嚟，部部插SIM卡之後都用得，於是齊齊問局長有乜創新科技可以裝到「安心出行」app，如果要強制市民裝app，拎部Nokia出街又冇裝app算唔算犯法？係咪會修例凡帶非智能電話出街即犯法？仲有網民話，好多長者專用嘅平安手機都冇得裝app，咁長者又點算？到時班公公婆婆無裝app無得去飲茶，又係製造民怨喇。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"a996824678db8b7430bcd3ae4c8993d0f0a7de38","tid":2297216,"uid":9694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:22:09.000Z","msg":"到時政府會幫冇智能手機既人做登記資料送中，然後每人送/租借一部紅米手機，由納稅人埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927147857eb1c583a411e486adc52c99092d8f75","tid":2297216,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a996824678db8b7430bcd3ae4c8993d0f0a7de38","tid":2297216,"uid":9694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:22:09.000Z","msg":"到時政府會幫冇智能手機既人做登記資料送中，然後每人送/租借一部紅米手機，由納稅人埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:29:11.000Z","msg":"大陸就係咁<br />\n基本上所有人都要手機先得<br />\n用非智能電話就街都唔洗出 野都冇得食<br />\n網購網閑魚連網頁版都執埋 淘寶想要優惠就要scan code<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd47340d3238353d89ed1a3c063aba6e5ede480","tid":2297216,"uid":350267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:32:25.000Z","msg":"全民Nokia<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43c9213b499804fbf4b835496061cd644618085","tid":2297216,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:34:42.000Z","msg":"手機唔係生活必需品，我冇手機的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/no